node.text: We’ve pushed the limits with Arctic Blast. Featuring bold strokes and a subtle ghosting of a hexagon pattern, it is painstakingly applied by hand. Words can’t describe the true beauty of this finish. Limited to a serialized edition of 500 Street Glide Special motorcycles. Learn more at the link in our bio.

node.text:
“It’s not about the destination, it’s about the journey. I just enjoy going.” - Andrew Y.

A bagger built for blasting off the line and long weekend rides, the 2021 Sport Glide is more than enough for even the most performance-hungry riders.

node.text:
Harley-Davidson commissioned one-of-a-kind Sportster S & Pan America helmet designs from Nuno Henriques, better known by @hellocousteau.​

Making a living designing a bit of everything, Nuno has carved out a diverse career in some of the world’s best design offices. After opening his own interior design office in Portugal in 2015, Nuno never thought the next step would be to design custom helmet graphics. Today, Nuno works with dozens of brands and private clients from around the world to create unique works of helmet art.
